Package: platedescribr
Title: Define, Read, and Visualize Experimental Conditions by Well for Well-Plate Assays
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Taiasean", "Wu", , "taiawu@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6988-1414"))
Description: An tidy approach to define the experimental conditions of each well in a well-plate assay. The user provides a plate layout file containing any number of experimental variables (e.g. "compound", "compound concentration", "protein"). The platedescribr package reads and tidies this file.
